Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ディソナス）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）うぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:47.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カブト）僕なんかに構ってて\Nいいのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんか\N大変なことになってるみたいだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カカシ）我々を甘く見るな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:58.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれも何とかなるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,クッ…　クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,（九尾）死ぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,（九尾）ここで死ぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:32.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,（九尾）つまらんやつめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:41.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフフフ…　貸してやるぞ　力を！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,《力…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:54.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ミナト：コントロールを…　力の…))
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:59.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,《力の…　コントロール…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サクラ）ナルト～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:09.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,《まだ…　終われねえ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:12.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ミナト：必ず出来る。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:17.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,(信じてるよ…　お前を…))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:23.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,たぁ～っ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:43.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～っ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～！　とりゃ～っ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:41.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サイ）すごい…。\N（ヤマト）だが…　九尾化じゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サクラ）ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,逃げたか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,ドックさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここは危険です！\N早く避難しないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ドック）でも…　あれを止めないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:16.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかっています。　我々に任せて…。\N（ドック）僕は→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:20.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,僕は　馘首になったけど\Nこの村の防人でした。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:25.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここを…　ホールを守るのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,僕の責任です。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:41.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,（シセル）一人じゃ無理。\Nダメだよ。　危険だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:46.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんの今の体力で\Nちゃ～んと　たどり着けるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,お願い…　一緒に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ミィナ）先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ファズ）行っちゃ　やだ。\N（レオ）行かないでよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）先生！\Nみんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:32.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,ファズ　好き嫌いは　もうダメよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,まずくても　贅沢言わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:39.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,力をうんとつけて\Nみんなを守って。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,ランド　年長らしく　しっかりな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:51.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなが困ってたら\N助け合って　頑張って。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ　みんなの世話をしてあげてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,ミィナの面倒　よくみてあげて。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,レオ　これからは\Nつらいことも悲しいことも→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:13.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,いっぱいあるかもしれないけど\Nみんなを支えて　頑張れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,ミィナちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,お願い　ミィナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの時　ひっぱたいて　ごめんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,ミィナだけが　ナルトお兄ちゃんが\Nおかしいことに気づいてたのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:39.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,わからなくて…　ごめんなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:43.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから　とても大変だと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　くじけないで　頑張って。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんや　みんなと一緒に→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,強く生きてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ミィナ）うわぁ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:11.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,短い間だったけど\N楽しかったよ　みんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,本当に幸せな時間だったわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:20.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　みんな。\Nありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,愛してるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:25.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,愛してるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,皆さん　子供たちをお願いします。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,はい。\N全力で守ります。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,シセル！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,シセルさん！\N先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ドック）もし…　もし\Nこれを生き延びられたら。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nもし　生き残れたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,結婚しよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:32.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっと言った。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:51.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　何が何でも\N生き残らなきゃね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,とぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハ…　ガハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:33.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ドック）あった！　さえずりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,あいつは　パターンの組み合わせだ\Nって言ってた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,どんな？\Nわかんないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうか…　ミィナのメロディーだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの子が　ずっと前から\N口ずさんでた　あれだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,殺せ　壊せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:42.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,世界のすべてを！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,これできっと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カカシ）ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:20.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！　まずい\N完全に我を失ってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,何！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,キャッ！\Nあっ　あぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ドック）シセル！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,シセル～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:07.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,うわぁ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,（３人）あっ！\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:24.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,早く登って。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:30.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダメ。　脱臼したみたい。\Nえぇっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラ　僕を回復してくれ。\N（サクラ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サイ）早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,すまない。\Nいえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ヤマト）でも　九尾の力が強すぎて→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,いつまで拘束できるか\Nわかりませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:12.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,苦しんでる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,ミィナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:37.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！　何か次の手を打たないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,負けないで。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:25.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん　もうやめて。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,覚悟はできてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:31.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,イヤだ。　離さない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:35.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,時間がないのよ。　私なんかより\N早く天の矛を止めて。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:41.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,絶対イヤだ。　僕の大好きな人が\Nまた落ちるのを見るなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう絶対イヤだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ドック）好きだったよ。\Nずっと　ずっと　ずっと。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:56.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから必死につかんでたのに\Nごめんよ。　ごめん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:59.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから　もう二度と離さない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,離すくらいなら一緒に落ちる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,私も　あん時から\Nずっと惚れてんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,私のほうが背が高くなっても→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:16.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,どんどん太っても\Nハゲても　グズでも臆病でも→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,私から逃げてばっかりでも。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:22.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,それでもやっぱり\Nずっと好きだったんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:31.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,でもね　あの子たちは誰が守るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:34.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,あなたしかいないの。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:38.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの子たちの未来は\Nあなたしか救えないの。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも…　でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:16.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,お願い　助けて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:22.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,((守りたい　助けたい\N大切な人たちを…　友達を…))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:33.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,パパと　ママを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ドック：信じてる。\N（ミナト）信じてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,(（ドック）キミの正しい力を。\N（ミナト）お前を…))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ランド）ナルト兄ちゃん！\N（ソラ）お願い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:46.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,助けて！\N僕たちの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）パパとママを！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,世界を救って。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:12.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの子たちを　守ってあげて。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:17.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,愛してる…　愛してるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,私の大切な…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ…　ナ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:15.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト君！？\Nおっちゃん　そいつを早く止めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:35.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,邪魔を…　するんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,おぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,うおぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,うおぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:04.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト兄ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト兄ちゃ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:19.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,おっ！　重てえって　ちょっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,助けてくれて　ありがとう　ナルト君。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:32.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,ありがとう。　本当に　ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:34.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:41.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,皆様　お変わりございませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:44.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,美空ひばりです。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:47.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,では　最後まで\Nごゆっくりお楽しみください。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:53.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,『木曜８時のコンサート\N名曲！　にっぽんの歌』→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:57.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,２時間スペシャル。\N今回は　ご覧の豪華な歌手の→
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:46.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should be\Nspending your time on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:51.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it seems like you've got\Nsome trouble on your hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:58.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do\Nsomething about that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That good-for-nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you some…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:40.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Power"…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Control…your "power."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Control my "power"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:00.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:08.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't…let it end here. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,in you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But…it's not\Nthe Nine Tails transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!\NYou must get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But…I must stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:14.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:20.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fired,\Nbut I used to be a village guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:25.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting this place…\Nthe "Hole"…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:45.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can get there\Nin your current condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– Sensei!\N– Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Faz, you can't be\Npicky anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain even\Nif it doesn't taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:38.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to become strong,\Nand look after everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Lando, you're the oldest,\Nso take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone's in trouble,\Nhelp them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, take care of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Mina…\NWatch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, there may be\Ntough times ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and sad times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But do your best to\Nhelp everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I slapped you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:34.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only one who sensed\Nthat Naruto wasn't himself…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will probably\Nget tough from here…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But hang in there and\Ndo your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you, your brother,\Nand the others…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,to be strong, and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't together too long,\Nbut it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They were such happy times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you…\NPlease look after the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do everything in our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiseru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– Sensei!\N– Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make it out of here alive…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:17.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make it out of here alive…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we're gonna get\Nthrough this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! The "Saezuri"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy said it was\Nthe combination of sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:38.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina's melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The one she's always been humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill… Destroy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This should work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:15.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely lost control\Nof himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiseru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiseru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry… Climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't… I think it's dislocated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura… Heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– Thanks!\N– Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nine Tails is too strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can\Nkeep restraining him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to try something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.69,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and stop\Nthe "Ama no Hoko"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:41.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to watch\Nthe person I love fall again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you! Since forever\Nand ever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I desperately\Nheld on, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:55.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll never let go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.82,english,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll fall together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love\Nwith you too, since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I grew taller…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.19,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And you kept getting fatter,\Nand lost your hair…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were indecisive\Nand scared of everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you kept turning away\Nfrom me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:22.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All that time, I still loved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But who's going to protect\Nthe children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:38.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who\Ncan save their future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But… But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please…save them…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:20.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To protect…my friends…{\i0}\N{\i1}those dear to me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to save my friends. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My papa and mama…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.44,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– {\i1}I believe in your power…{\i0}\N– {\i1}in the good inside you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.03,english